id = "off_the_bus"
display_name = "The Small-Town Transplant"
title = "Off the Bus"
blurb = "Population 312 to population 80,000. You have a duffel bag, sturdy boots, and a cousin's address that turned out to be fake.

+ Clean Slate: nobody's chasing you. Honest face. Hard worker (+10% job skill XP).
- You know NOBODY. Naive to city scams. No skills above baseline.

The tutorial life: lowest highs, highest floor."
